subject: ADT Championship (Golf)
Golf
lead_paragraph: Ji-Yai Shin, a 20-year-old from South Korea, defeated Karrie Webb, a L.P.G.A. Hall of Famer 13 years her senior, by one stroke to win the ADT Championship.
